{"PRIAL":[{"def":"A corruption of pair royal.","pos":""}],"PRIAN":[{"def":"A fine, white, somewhat friable clay; also, the ore contained in a mixture of clay and pebbles.","pos":""}],"PRIAPISM":[{"def":"More or less permanent erection and rigidity of the penis, with or without sexual desire.","pos":""}],"PRIAPULACEA":[{"def":"A suborder of Gephyræa, having a cylindrical body with a terminal anal opening, and usually with one or two caudal gills.","pos":""}]}